rogramming]]\n[[Category:English-language television programs]]\n[[Category:NBC original programming]]\n[[Category:Television series by Sony Pictures Television]]\n[[Category:Sony Pictures Television franchises]]\n[[Category:Television shows set in New York City]]\n[[Category:American television series revived after cancellation]]\n[[Category:Works about adoption]]\n[[Category:Television series about siblings]]\n[[Category:The Facts of Life (TV series)]]\n[[Category:Television series about families]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Television series}}\n{{more citations needed|date=January 2009}}\n{{Infobox television\n| show_name                = Diff'rent Strokes\n| image                    = diffrentstrokes.jpg\n| caption                  = Title screen\n| genre                    = [[Sitcom]]\n| creator                  = Jeff Harris<br />[[Bernie Kukoff]]\n| writer                   = [[Ben Starr (American producer)|Ben Starr]]<br />Budd Grossman<br />[[Howard Leeds]]<br />[[Martin Cohan]]\n| director                 = [[Herbert Kenwith]]<br /><small>(season 1)</small><br />[[Gerren Keith]]<br />[[Mel Ferber]]<br />[[Tony Singletary]]\n| starring                 = [[Conrad Bain]]<br />[[Gary Coleman]]<br />[[Todd Bridges]]<br />[[Dana Plato]]<br />[[Charlotte Rae]]<br />[[Nedra Volz]]<br />[[Mary Jo Catlett]]<br />[[Shavar Ross]]<br />[[Janet Jackson]]<br />[[Dixie Carter]]<br />[[Mary Ann Mobley]]<br />[[Danny Cooksey]]\n| theme_music_composer     = [[Alan Thicke]]<br />Al Burton<br />[[Gloria Loring]]\n| opentheme                = \"It Takes Diff'rent Strokes\"\n| composer                 = \n| country                  = United States\n| language                 = English\n| num_seasons              = 8\n| num_episodes             = 189\n| list_episodes            = List of Diff'rent Strokes episodes\n| executive_producer       = Budd Grossman<br /><small>(season 1)</small><br />[[Howard Leeds]]<br /><small>(seasons 2\u20136)</small><br />[[Blake Hunter]]